title: What is this Icon and why do I have it?
body:
This pumpkin icon was given to me by riot today 11/17/16

Someone pls explain

replies.body: That is the pumpkin icon that was rewarded from the [Teemoing](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016).  This one was for gifting someone during the event.  Grats!
The pumpkin icon was given to you because you sent a gift to someone during the Teemoing event.
